sys/memory/garbage_collection/mark_sweep.runa
Mark and Sweep Garbage Collection

This module provides mark and sweep garbage collection implementation.
Includes support for mark phase traversal, sweep phase reclamation,
and optimized mark-sweep variants with tri-color marking.
